reviewText: We have purchased Series 1-3 and love all of them.  Highly recommended.  Characters and story lines are charming.

Having just discovered "Peak Practice" through a friend, I eagerly anticipated the series arrival. From the very first episode I was hooked and have enjoyed watching numerous reruns. Can't wait to get Series 2 and 3. Even though it's advertised as non USA format I can watch it on my region 1 laptop.
I wish there would come more of this show to USA,I see this in Denmark,and wish we could get it here also. So let us get more dvd of this show to the USA.
